This is a pytorch implementation of Sawn.

Install:
conda create -name sawn python=3.6
pip install -r requirement.txt
bash ./setup.sh

Training
1) Flow Field Pretraining:
bash scripts/train_FlowField.sh

2) Sawn Training:
bash scripts/train_Sawn.sh

3) STPR Training for texture transfer:
bash scripts/train_STPR.sh

Test:
bash scripts/test_pose_transfer.sh
bash scripts/test_texture_transfer.sh

Reference code:

[1] https://github.com/RenYurui/Global-Flow-Local-Attention
[2] https://github.com/NVlabs/SPADE